{"title":"vue","date":"2019-03-12T16:16:11.000Z","slug":"vue","tags":["vue 模板语法","阅读文档"],"updated":"2019-03-13T08:20:19.920Z","content":"<h3 id=\"vue-模板语法\">vue 模板语法<a href=\"post/vue#vue-模板语法\"></a></h3><h5 id=\"文本\">文本<a href=\"post/vue#文本\"></a></h5><blockquote>\n<p>  <code>msg</code> 会被替换成 <code>data</code> 对象中的<code>msg属性的值</code><br><figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">span</span>&gt;</span>Message: &#123;&#123; msg &#125;&#125;<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">span</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">script</span>&gt;</span><span class=\"undefined\"></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"undefined\">    var vm = new Vue (&#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"undefined\">        data :&#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"undefined\">            msg: '文本'</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"undefined\">        &#125;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"undefined\">    &#125;)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"undefined\"></span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">script</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p>通过<code>v-once</code> 可以<code>只执行一次渲染</code>，当 data数据对象中的 <code>msg的值发生时</code>，模板中 msg 的内容不改变还是<code>第一次渲染时的值</code></p>\n</blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>v-once 会影响到该节点上的其他数据绑定<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">span</span> <span class=\"attr\">v-once</span> &gt;</span>我还是最初的我: &#123;&#123; msg &#125;&#125;<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">span</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">script</span> &gt;</span><span class=\"undefined\"></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"undefined\">     var vm = new Vue (&#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"undefined\">        data :&#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"undefined\">            msg: '文本'</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"undefined\">        &#125;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"undefined\">     &#125;)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"undefined\">     vm.$data.msg  = '我还是最初的我'</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"undefined\"></span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">script</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n</ul>\n","prev":{"title":"git","slug":"git"},"next":{"title":"flex","slug":"flex"},"link":"https://meizizit.github.io/post/vue/"}